content.rendered:
Directed by Shridhar Shikaripura

Written by Shridhar Shikaripura

Cast Naveen Shankar (Adhi). Aishani Shetty (Shreya). Yash Shetty (Shivu). Balarajwadi (Antony). Siddu Moolimani (Parachut). Omkar Aryaa (Disco (as Omkar)). Nitesh Mahan (Slow Motion Seena). Jayashree Aradhya (Ambuja). Mohan Juneja (Desai).Ugramm Ravi

Language Kannada

Producers Omkar Aryaa. Sanju Gandhi. K Gowthami Reddy. Srinivas Sagar.
